      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This example is mechanically robust, having received essential preventative maintenance including VANOS system servicing and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis longevity. The suspension retains its factory-tuned balance with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, providing communicative hydraulic steering feedback. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the powertrain remains potent and the throttle response is exceptionally linear. A well-sorted icon for the purist looking for visceral performance.",
